snippet.title: 3 NEW CLASH Games Announcement!
snippet.description:
Visit 👉 https://clash.com 👈 and sign up to get notified when these games are available in your country! 

We're excited to announce 3 new Clash games in development: Clash Quest, Clash Mini and Clash Heroes! 

Announcement blog: http://supr.cl/3cJ6MXr

Follow each Clash game on our Socials!
